requriement 
1 performance
	200-300 hit/seconds to app server
	500-800 hit/seconds to web server
	
2 data
	separate collecting server and user facing server
	how do they talk to each other. create a view, write separately.
	production server running on 		
	
	server will have House as a table, PHouse as a view with only oked data
	
	client will have House as a table without PK.
	
	client will have the /service/sync url opened,
	/service/sync?action=history showing history of all syncs
	/service/sync?action=status showing status of current syncs
	/service/sync?action=trigger start a new sync
	
	sync will run every 15 minutes
	
	in config file there will be a variable called IS_SERVER, indicating whether or not this is a server
	
    	
